oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Emiko holding Robert Yates Kinsall
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of Emiko holding Robert Yates Kinsall on the front porch of the Kinsall home in Nagoya, Japan. Robert, aged 2, is the son of Lt. Col. J.Y. Yates and his wife Elizabeth Ann Aker. Emiko, along with her sister Yasko, were governess for the Kinsall family while Lt. Col. J.Y. Kinsall was stationed at Nagoya Air Base.
